How to be annonymous on kali linux 

Tool : proxychains
1) sudo nano /etc/proxychains.conf
2) uncomment dynamic_chain
3) make sure proxy_dns is uncommeneted
4) add the below IP 
>> socks5 127.0.0.1 9050 

socks5 is more advance and secure than socks4. 
All your traffic will be routed through tor network

>> sudo apt install tor (if not installed)
>> sudo service tor start

Open any browser or run any program

>> proxychains firefox duckduckgo.com
>> proxychains nmap --
